  <process-def name=":AutoPilot-OA-Storage_Management:LUN:Resize LUN">
    <parameters>
      <input global="false" required="true">
        <description>Name of the storage vendor.  Supported vendors: NetApp, EMC</description>
        <from>configuration name</from>
        <to>configuration name</to>
      </input>
      <input global="false" required="true">
        <description>NetApp
Sample Items XML:

&lt;storage&gt;
	&lt;target-host&gt;devsim1&lt;/target-host&gt;
	&lt;force&gt;true&lt;/force&gt;
	&lt;path&gt;san_dataset_2/lun1/lun1&lt;/path&gt;
	&lt;size&gt;40000000&lt;/size&gt;
     &lt;storage-unit&gt;GB&lt;/storage-unit&gt;
&lt;/storage&gt;

Parameters Description:

target-host [Required]
	The hostname or IP of the target storage/filer.

force [Optional]
	Forcibly reduce the size. This is required for reducing the size of the LUN to avoid accidentally reducing the LUN size.

path [Required]
	Path of the LUN.

size [Required]
	New size for the LUN.

storage-unit [Required]
     Valid Values:MB, GB, TB, KB

EMC:
sample xml
&lt;storage&gt;
 &lt;storage-system-name&gt; &lt;/storage-system-name&gt;
  &lt;lun-name&gt;LUN 30 &lt;/lun-name&gt;
  &lt;size&gt; 20 &lt;/size&gt;
	&lt;storage-unit&gt;MB&lt;/storgae-unit&gt;
   &lt;composite-type&gt;2&lt;/composite-type&gt;
&lt;/storage&gt;

Parameter description
storage-system-name [Requiredl]:
-----------------------------------------

	- Specifies the storage system name from which the information has to be collected.
	- Valid value: Any valid string.
	- Default value: None.
	
lun-name [Required]:
-------------------------

	- Specifies the lun names that have to be expanded.
	- Valid value: None.
	- Default value: None.

size [Required]:
--------------------

	- Specifies the size that should be expanded.
	- Valid value: numeric value.
	- Default value: None.
----------------------------------------------
storage-unit [Required]
     Valid Values:MB, GB, TB, KB
--------------------------------------------------------
composite-type [optional]:
-----------------------------------------

	- Specifies the type of composite element to create 
     - Valid value: 
             2 -&gt; Concatenate element
             3 -&gt; Stripe element   
      - Default value: null
</description>
        <from>storage</from>
        <to>storage</to>
      </input>
